{
  "description": "A long-distance shot of Alcatraz Island and the Golden Gate Bridge in San Francisco Bay. Alcatraz Island is prominently featured in the foreground, appearing as a dark, rectangular mass surrounded by water. In the background, the iconic Golden Gate Bridge spans the bay, its red-orange towers and cables visible but somewhat muted due to distance and atmospheric haze. An airplane is captured mid-flight, passing directly beneath the bridge's suspension cables, adding a sense of scale and movement. Numerous small boats and sailboats dot the water, creating a bustling maritime scene. The overall tone is muted and hazy, creating a slightly ethereal effect.",
